Including Plots

You can also embed plots, for example:

set.seed(1)
huatu <- data.frame(a = sample(10), out = c(1, 3, 2, 4, 5, 7, 6, 8, 9, 10))

nn_huatu <- neuralnet(out ~ a, data = huatu, hidden = c(21, 8, 8), algorithm = "backprop", 
    linear.output = T, learningrate = 0.01, stepmax = 10000000, threshold = 0.3)
library(NeuralNetTools)
# plot(nn_huatu)
plotnet(nn_huatu, nid = T, struct = c(0, 21, 8, 8, 1), circle_col = "lightgreen")
